Deep Dish Delight

Michael hits the road, heading to Chicago for a taste of world renowned deep dish pizza. Then, he hits up San Francisco, where people are lining up for hours at a dim sum style hot spot for local, California cuisine. The next stop is Las Vegas, for a celebrity chefs famous banana cream pie. Michael makes a final stop in Austin for exotic sausages with crazy, unique toppings.
